Articles.Content:
Hello KSP Players,

today i wanted to switch to a vessel that i launched about 30 kerbin days ago and everything disappeared space center kerbin etc. And even a quickload couldnt solve this so i had to delete my whole savegame.

Im using these mods:

Spoiler

-Astroidday

-Contractconfigurator

-Contractpack (Space Station Building)

-CxAerospace station parts

-DMagicOrbitalScience

-Firespitter

-Rasterpropmonitor

-Kerbal Attachment System

-Kerbal Joint Reinforcement

-Hyperedit

-Kerbal Inventory System

-Klockheed Martian Gimbal

-KSO Orbiter

-KW Rocketry + Community Fix (1.0.5)

-Mechjeb

-Near Future Solar

-Smokescreen

-SXT Airbags

-Tacfuelbalancer

-Tarsierspacetech

-Trajectories

-Tweakscale

What mods are causing this bug or what am i doing wrong?

Greetings

Dustin Fischer
